race.description: Ladbrokes Srm In Multis Mdn Plate
race.comment: JENNI GONE BONKERS (6) resumes. Her form last time in reads very well, just finding one better in three runs in a row, beaten under a length in a Listed race behind the smart Sunrays at Eagle Farm before a spell. She's won a trial very well leading in and should go close. WYANDRA (5) has run second in all three runs to date, stepping up to this trip at Sale last time and trying hard all the way to the line when beaten a nose. Sets up ideally from the gate here and has race fitness on his side. GEESEVEN (2) is a gelding by Bivouac on debut for the Begg yard who has won a jumpout leading in. Have to respect the top stable, keep safe. WINSILENCE (4) is a gelding by Ghaiyyath on debut for the Hayes yard who has to be respected off a jumpout win. BEST TERMS (1) is a Maurice gelding on debut who can run well.
